AddonId: 'UniPlaySong.a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890'
Type: Generic
Name: 'UniPlaySong'
Author: 'Huddini'
ShortDescription: 'Console-like game music preview experience with controller support and audio management features. Music plays when selecting games in your library.'
InstallerManifestUrl: 'https://github.com/aHuddini/UniPlaySong/releases/latest/download/installer.yaml'
SourceUrl: 'https://github.com/aHuddini/UniPlaySong'
Description: |
  UniPlaySong provides a console-like game music preview experience and controller-friendly song management for Playnite. 
  
  Key Features:
  - Automatic music playback when selecting games in your library
  - Fullscreen Xbox controller support for complete music management from your couch
  - Audio normalization tools using FFmpeg (EBU R128 standard)
  - Trimming tools to change song start position
  - Download music directly from online sources manually or automatically
  - Customizable fade transitions, preview times, and randomization
  - Primary song system for setting default tracks on Playnite boot
  - Default/fallback music support for games with no music
  - Works seamlessly with all Playnite themes (desktop and fullscreen)
  
  Designed for both Desktop and Fullscreen mode, with compatibility to modern themes like ANIKI REMAKE.
